Regulation (EEC) No 2915/79 is hereby amended as follows:
1. In Article 11 (5), 'For 1984' is deleted;
2. In Annex II:
(a) the text of (b) under the first indent of point (c) is replaced by the following:
'(b) 6 250 tonnes, including the quota of Finlandia referred to in point (q), originating in Finland;'
(b) '1 350 tonnes' in (b) under the second indent of point (c) is replaced by '1 600 tonnes';
(c) '500 tonnes' in (b) of point (h) is replaced by '550 tonnes';
(d) 'in respect of 1984' in point (s) is deleted.
